Here are my edits of Wildest Dreams (Taylor's Version) and Bad Blood (Taylor's Version) to recreate their original radio edits. I wanted to make sure to keep as much percussion from the original Taylor's Version of Wildest Dreams that I could, but add the sparkle that made the original Radio Edit so special.

I also updated the Bad Blood edit from my original posted version. This one has a lot less filtered artifacts / sounds closer to the official.

Please don't repost to any other websites / upload them to YouTube.​
